{
  "texts": [
    "Of course, it must also not be accompanied by the intentions characterised by an honest utterance.",
    "So far this story is entirely negative.",
    "Must any positive intentions be manifested in the utterer?",
    "Throughout most of Frankfurt's discussion, his characterisation of bullshit is negative.",
    "He notes that bullshit requires \"no conviction\" from the speaker about what the truth is (2005: 55), that the bullshitter \"pays no attention\" to the truth (2005: 61) and that they \"may not deceive us, or even intend to do so, either about the facts or what he takes the facts to be\" (2005: 54)."
  ]
}